title: NFL Preseason 2013 Super Bowl XLVIII Seahawks and Broncos
description:
NFL Preseason games from week#3 recorded in HDTV format 1920x1080 featuring Seahawks and Broncos who will be matched at Super Bowl XLVIII on Sunday, FEBRUARY 2, 2014!


Seattle Seahawks at Green Bay Packers (Preseason Week 3 played back on Friday, August 23, 2013)

St. Louis Rams at Denver Broncos (Preseason Week 3 played back on Saturday, August 24, 2013)




Commercials have been REMOVED and default audio is http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parabolic_microphone capturing game sound only.  Announcer audio is selectable in the mkv as audio#2 if you really need to listen to these idiots!



Wish we COULD have the option to watch Super Bowl XLVIII this way!
